---
import FadeIn from "./FadeIn";
---
<section class="py-12 md:py-16 xl:py-24 relative overflow-hidden">

  <div class="container px-4 md:px-6 relative z-10">
    <FadeIn delay={100} client:visible>
      <div class="max-w-[900px] mx-auto rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 text-center border-2 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-white/15 to-white/5 border-amber-400/40 relative">
        
        <!-- Urgency badge at top -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-red-500/25 border-2 border-red-400/50 rounded-full px-4 py-2 mb-6 animate-pulse">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#ff0000">
            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V7h2v6z"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm md:text-base font-bold text-red-100">Solo quedan 23 unidades en stock</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Main headline - More direct and urgent -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl xl:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4 leading-tight">
          Recupera Tu Sueño <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-300 to-orange-400">Esta Misma Noche</span>
        </h2>
        
        <!-- Subheadline - Benefit-focused with social proof -->
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl xl:text-2xl mb-3 text-gray-100 font-semibold">
          Más de 3,000 colombianos ya duermen mejor y trabajan sin fatiga
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg mb-8 text-gray-200 max-w-[700px] mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          No más noches en vela. No más dolores de cabeza. Solo descanso profundo y ojos protegidos — <strong class="text-white">desde tu primera noche usando Amber Vision</strong>.
        </p>

        <!-- Main CTA Button - Enhanced -->
        <div class="mb-6">
          <a
            href="#pricing"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 via-orange-500 to-red-500 hover:from-amber-400 hover:via-orange-400 hover:to-red-400 px-2 py-4 md:px-10 md:py-6 rounded-xl shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-amber-500/50 text-white font-bold text-lg md:text-xl group relative overflow-hidden"
          >
            <!-- Animated shine effect -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent translate-x-[-100%] group-hover:translate-x-[100%] transition-transform duration-1000 gap-2"></div>
            
            <span class="relative z-10">Ver Precios y Opciones</span>
        
            <svg
              class="relative z-10 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
            >
              <path d="M6 19m-2 0a2 2 0 1 0 4 0a2 2 0 1 0 -4 0" />
              <path d="M17 19m-2 0a2 2 0 1 0 4 0a2 2 0 1 0 -4 0" />
              <path d="M17 17h-11v-14h-2" />
              <path d="M6 5l14 1l-1 7h-13" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Secondary micro-CTA text -->
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base mb-8 text-amber-200 font-semibold">
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base mb-8 text-amber-200 font-semibold">
  ⚡ Envío express disponible — Recíbelas en 24-48 horas y empieza a dormir mejor
</p>
        </p>

        <!-- Trust badges - Enhanced with specifics -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-300">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                  <svg
                    width="16"
                    height="16"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="#10b981"
                    stroke-width="2"
                  >
                    <path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>Envío gratis</span>
                </div>

                <span class="text-gray-600">•</span>

                <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                  <svg
                    width="16"
                    height="16"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="#10b981"
                    stroke-width="2"
                  >
                    <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>30 días de garantía</span>
                </div>

                <span class="text-gray-600">•</span>

                <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                  <svg
                    width="16"
                    height="16"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="#10b981"
                    stroke-width="2"
                  >
                    <path d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>Pago 100% seguro</span>
                </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </FadeIn>
  </div>
</section>